      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TRANSFORMATION (7) was out of the placings last time but before that was an impressive winner (22.45) in a Maiden at Shepparton. Solid beginner and with a good start should have clear running out wide. Meets a moderate line up and rates on top this time. HOOKED ON DREAMS (2) settled down midfield and held his position to the line when finishing 5th (20.21) at this track. Has ability and can measure up. ULTIMATE (1) was midfield throughout and finished there last time when 4th (20.16) at this track. Good beginner assisted by the inside draw. One of the better chances. ONCE A DIVA (8) made it two minor placings on the trot when beaten third (20.16) in a TG1-4W at this track last time out. Safe beginner but wide box to overcome and will need some luck.",
